{
  "name": "VK Content Creation Workflow",
  "nodes": [
    {
      "parameters": {
        "rule": {
          "interval": [
            {
              "field": "hours",
              "hoursInterval": 2
            }
          ]
        }
      },
      "id": "schedule-trigger",
      "name": "Schedule Trigger",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.scheduleTrigger",
      "typeVersion": 1.1,
      "position": [
        240,
        300
      ]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "httpMethod": "POST",
        "path": "create-vk-post",
        "options": {}
      },
      "id": "webhook-trigger",
      "name": "Webhook Trigger",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.webhook",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [
        240,
        500
      ],
      "webhookId": "vk-content-webhook"
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## VK Content Creation Workflow\n\nThis workflow can be triggered:\n1. By schedule (every 2 hours)\n2. Via webhook POST to /create-vk-post\n\n### Webhook Payload Example:\n```json\n{\n  \"message\": \"Your post text here\",\n  \"attachments\": [\"photo123_456\"],\n  \"publish_date\": \"2026-02-07T12:00:00\",\n  \"from_group\": 1\n}\n```",
        "height": 464,
        "width": 567
      },
      "id": "sticky-note",
      "name": "Sticky Note",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [
        -20,
        240
      ]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "conditions": {
          "string": [
            {
              "value1": "={{ $json.message }}",
              "operation": "isNotEmpty"
            }
          ]
        }
      },
      "id": "check-content",
      "name": "Check Content",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.if",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [
        460,
        400
      ]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "jsCode": "// Process and prepare VK post data\nconst inputData = $input.all();\nconst processedItems = [];\n\nfor (const item of inputData) {\n  const data = item.json;\n  \n  // Default values\n  const postData = {\n    message: data.message || '',\n    attachments: data.attachments || [],\n    from_group: data.from_group || 1,\n    publish_date: data.publish_date || null,\n    lat: data.lat || null,\n    long: data.long || null,\n    place_id: data.place_id || null,\n    post_id: data.post_id || null,\n    guid: data.guid || Date.now().toString(),\n    mark_as_ads: data.mark_as_ads || 0,\n    close_comments: data.close_comments || 0,\n    mute_notifications: data.mute_notifications || 0,\n    copyright: data.copyright || null\n  };\n  \n  // Add hashtags if provided\n  if (data.hashtags && Array.isArray(data.hashtags)) {\n    postData.message += '\\n\\n' + data.hashtags.map(tag => `#${tag}`).join(' ');\n  }\n  \n  // Format publish date if provided\n  if (postData.publish_date) {\n    const date = new Date(postData.publish_date);\n    postData.publish_date = Math.floor(date.getTime() / 1000);\n  }\n  \n  processedItems.push({\n    json: postData,\n    pairedItem: item.pairedItem\n  });\n}\n\nreturn processedItems;"
      },
      "id": "process-data",
      "name": "Process Data",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.code",
      "typeVersion": 2,
      "position": [
        680,
        300
      ]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "authentication": "oAuth2",
        "resource": "post",
        "operation": "create",
        "owner": "={{ $json.owner_id }}",
        "message": "={{ $json.message }}",
        "additionalFields": {
          "attachments": "={{ $json.attachments.join(',') }}",
          "from_group": "={{ $json.from_group }}",
          "publish_date": "={{ $json.publish_date }}",
          "lat": "={{ $json.lat }}",
          "long": "={{ $json.long }}",
          "place_id": "={{ $json.place_id }}",
          "post_id": "={{ $json.post_id }}",
          "guid": "={{ $json.guid }}",
          "mark_as_ads": "={{ $json.mark_as_ads }}",
          "close_comments": "={{ $json.close_comments }}",
          "mute_notifications": "={{ $json.mute_notifications }}"
        }
      },
      "id": "vk-post",
      "name": "Create VK Post",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.vk",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [
        900,
        300
      ],
      "credentials": {
        "vkOAuth2Api": {
          "id": "1",
          "name": "VK OAuth2 API"
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "operation": "executeQuery",
        "query": "INSERT INTO vk_posts (post_id, message, created_at, status) VALUES ({{ $json.post_id }}, '{{ $json.message }}', NOW(), 'published')",
        "options": {}
      },
      "id": "log-to-db",
      "name": "Log to Database",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.postgres",
      "typeVersion": 2.3,
      "position": [
        1120,
        300
      ],
      "credentials": {
        "postgres": {
          "id": "2",
          "name": "PostgreSQL"
        }
      },
      "disabled": true
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "method": "POST",
        "url": "={{ $json.webhook_url }}",
        "authentication": "genericCredentialType",
        "genericAuthType": "httpHeaderAuth",
        "sendBody": true,
        "bodyParameters": {
          "parameters": [
            {
              "name": "status",
              "value": "success"
            },
            {
              "name": "post_id",
              "value": "={{ $json.post_id }}"
            },
            {
              "name": "message",
              "value": "Post published successfully"
            }
          ]
        },
        "options": {}
      },
      "id": "notify-success",
      "name": "Notify Success",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.httpRequest",
      "typeVersion": 4.1,
      "position": [
        1120,
        180
      ],
      "disabled": true
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## Error Handler\n\nCatches errors and sends notifications",
        "height": 233,
        "width": 240
      },
      "id": "error-note",
      "name": "Error Note",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [
        600,
        540
      ]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "method": "POST",
        "url": "={{ $json.error_webhook_url }}",
        "sendBody": true,
        "bodyParameters": {
          "parameters": [
            {
              "name": "status",
              "value": "error"
            },
            {
              "name": "error",
              "value": "={{ $json.error }}"
            },
            {
              "name": "timestamp",
              "value": "={{ $now }}"
            }
          ]
        },
        "options": {}
      },
      "id": "notify-error",
      "name": "Notify Error",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.httpRequest",
      "typeVersion": 4.1,
      "position": [
        680,
        500
      ],
      "disabled": true
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "assignments": {
          "assignments": [
            {
              "id": "error-msg",
              "name": "error",
              "value": "Content validation failed: message is empty",
              "type": "string"
            }
          ]
        },
        "options": {}
      },
      "id": "set-error",
      "name": "Set Error",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.set",
      "typeVersion": 3.3,
      "position": [
        680,
        500
      ]
    }
  ],
  "connections": {
    "Schedule Trigger": {
      "main": [
        [
          {
            "node": "Check Content",
            "type": "main",
            "index": 0
          }
        ]
      ]
    },
    "Webhook Trigger": {
      "main": [
        [
          {
            "node": "Check Content",
            "type": "main",
            "index": 0
          }
        ]
      ]
